item.title: E02457
item.description: Joy (Gardner Denver) WB12 6.5”x5.0” Single-Stage skid mounted air booster, can boost air up to 2300 CFM (65.13 m3/min). It can go to 50 bar. c/w Cat 3406 engine. Engine and compressor are in good and clean condition.

item.title: E03940
item.description: Atlas Copco XA350 Ex-Army towable aircompressor, 8 cylinder Deutz F8L413F aircooled engine, advised working pressure 8 Bar, 740CFM (21.0 M3/min) free air delivery, Michelin 7.50R16 XCL tyres 85% remaining. Compressor comes straight out of work, has low hours and is in clean condition. Compressor can be painted in company colours or original Atlas Copco colours at extra cost. Inspections are welcome.
